Clafer-vim ver. 1
=================
Integration of Clafer into VIM editing environment

CONTRIBUTORS
============
Andrzej WÄ…sowski

FEATURES
========
* syntax highlighting for structural Clafer
* syntax highlighting for behavioral Clafer

INSTALLATION
============
Please use a package manager.  This plugin should work with
pathogen (https://github.com/tpope/vim-pathogen) and vundle
(https://github.com/gmarik/Vundle.vim). The plugin is tested
with vundle.

